net.sf.jclec.mo.experiment.handler

Class GenerateReferencePF

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.mo.experiment.handler.MOExperimentHandler
      • net.sf.jclec.mo.experiment.handler.GenerateReferencePF

  • public class GenerateReferencePF
extends MOExperimentHandler
    This handler constructs a reference Pareto front from a set of fronts returned by different algorithms.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    1.0
